1.title: Snowy Boston to Sunny Vieques
1.plot: A Boston man with a stressful job leaves the snowy city for the outdoor activities and tropical lifestyle in Vieques, Puerto Rico.

4.title: Raising Two Boys on St. Croix
4.plot: A couple follows a job to St. Croix, US Virgin Islands, and hopes to find a house with a big backyard, a pool and a lookout where they can stargaze in the beautiful Caribbean sky.

5.title: Healthy Living on St. Croix
5.plot: A couple leaves the hectic city of Tampa, FL, and starts a brand new healthy lifestyle in St. Croix, US Virgin Islands.

1.title: A Couple from Minnesota Looks for a Dream Home in Vieques
1.plot: Karrin and John Pecchia and their two little girls have called it quits on the Minnesota cold and are moving down to a land of sand, sun and water. Their lives are about to be filled with Punta Cana's sand castles and palm trees.

2.title: A Family Leaves the Freezing Cold of Vermont, for the Tropical Climate of Vieques, Puerto Rico
2.plot: Margi and Jessi La Porte have been living off the grid in cold Vermont for the majority of their lives. On a recent vacation to Vieques the couple completely fell in love with the island and decided to make their stay permanent.

3.title: A Family from St. Louis Looks for Their Dream Home on St. Croix
3.plot: Dave and Julie moved from St. Louis to St. Croix in 2006, but their cramped rental isn't cutting it anymore now that their family has grown by 3. Agent Chris Hanley helps them find a home with a large yard close to the yacht club.

4.title: A Couple Is Looking to Settle Down by Buying Their First House Together in St. Croix
4.plot: Corinne Farinola and Patrick Kralik moved to the Caribbean from PA and SC respectively. They fell in love in St. Croix. After renting, the couple's ready for the next step in their relationship - buying a home together.

5.plot: Johnny Kelvin and Ona Struwer are world traveling DJs having been to every corner of the planet. They're ready to find a place to call home base on the island of Sint Maarten because of its warm beaches and energy from its people.

6.plot: The cold New England winters had gotten to Cliff and Janine Peek, so they decided to escape the Caribbean. Avid boaters, the Peeks are drawn to the yachting in Sint Maarten and hope to find something on the island's Dutch side.

7.plot: Griselle and Steve Mucccilo have lived on Long Island for the past 17 years. After many years in high stress jobs, they have decided to get off the rat race treadmill and move to Puerto Rico. They've decided to relocate to Rincon.

8.plot: Omar Del Rio is from San Juan, Puerto Rico and Caroline Crouch, his girlfriend is from Chicago. These two lovebirds found each other by chance in San Juan and are in search of country life on the island paradise of Puerto Rico.

1.title: A Pennsylvania Family Moves to Puerto Rico for Culture, Sun and Local Cuisine

5.plot: Married for ten years, Billy and Deanna own and run a popular BBQ restaurant in WV. They discovered St. Croix by way of food. Years ago, they were part of a team that traveled to the island to work with fellow chefs.

6.title: Busy New Yorkers Move to St. Croix to Open an Events and Catering Business
6.plot: A busy family trades the streets of New York City for the calm waters of St. Croix.

7.plot: Matt and Kristy are about to get married. They went to high school together and, twelve years after graduation, they started dating and are now engaged. They're tired of the daily grind and brutal winters and look to St. Croix.

8.plot: Amy, Marc and their four kids considered themselves Midwest lifers. But when Marc's company offered him a chance to relocate to their St. Croix office, the couple decided to tmove to St. Croix.

9.title: A Los Angeles family of four trades in their cars for boats and move to Bocas Del Toro, Panama
9.plot: Scott, Lauren and their two kids are tired of the daily grind of Los Angeles. Lauren, a freelance photographer, and Scott, a freelance software engineer, recently visited friends living in Bocas Del Toro, Panama, and fell in love.

10.title: A couple trades in their Seattle lives and careers to start their own business in Bocas Del Toro
10.plot: Fifteen years in Seattle has left John, a financial analyst, and his wife Janaea, a sales director, worn down. So they're moving to Bocas Del Toro, Panama, to start life anew. They plan to open a day cruise business.

11.title: A Colorado family leaves snowy Fort Collins for the Caribbean life in Bocas Del Toro, Panama
11.plot: When still single, Riley's older sister landed a job in Bocas Del Toro, Panama. Riley was all set to join her sister, but fell in love when she met Matt. Six years, two kids later, Riley's ready move for real to Bocas Del Toro.

12.plot: A family follows their hearts from Texas to Roatan, Honduras.

14.title: A couple leaves landlocked Austin, Texas for a dream life in Roatan, Honduras
14.plot: Jay and Lavina are tired of landlocked Texas. They love scuba diving more than anything, and the state's shallow pools, murky waters and long drives to bodies of water have become too much of a compromise.

1.title: A Canadian Family, Originally from the Caribbean, Escapes the Snow for Life in Barbados.

8.plot: A Los Angeles TV executive returns to his roots and sets up a production company in the Cayman Islands.

9.plot: A Texas family says adios to traffic and hello to sand, sun and fun in the Dominican Republic.

imdb.plot outline: Follow families as they leave the mainland behind and head to the Caribbean to live on island time. Join their search for an affordable slice of heaven, touring gorgeous homes on white sandy beaches. You don't have be rich to live in paradise!
